---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Tutorials
description: Build-along tutorials from We Can Build.
permalink: /tutorials/index.html
---

<div class="head">
  <p class="eyebrow">The series so far</p>
  <h1>Build-along tutorials</h1>
  <p>I'm just getting started, so the shape of this is still up for grabs. The live posts are below, followed by a handful of ideas I'm thinking about. The order might change, the list might change, and some of these might turn into something else entirely.</p>
</div>

<div class="grid">
  {% for post in collections.posts | reverse %}
  <div class="post">
    <div class="thumb">
      {% if post.data.youtubeId %}
        <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/{{ post.data.youtubeId }}" title="{{ post.data.title }}" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe>
      {% elif post.data.cover %}
        <img src="{{ post.data.cover }}" alt="{{ post.data.title }}" />
      {% else %}
        [ cover image ]
      {% endif %}
    </div>
    <div class="body">
      <div class="row">
        <span class="k">{{ post.data.label or 'Tutorial' }}</span>
        <span class="pill live">{{ post.data.status or 'New' }}</span>
      </div>
      <h3>{{ post.data.title }}</h3>
      <p>{{ post.data.summary }}</p>
      <div class="row" style="justify-content:space-between;margin:0;">
        <span class="meta">{{ post.date | readableDate }}{% if post.data.readTime %} &middot; {{ post.data.readTime }}{% endif %}</span>
        <a class="read" href="{{ post.url }}">Read &rarr;</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  {% endfor %}

  {% for stub in upcoming %}
  <div class="post stub">
    <div class="thumb">Not built yet</div>
    <div class="body">
      <div class="row"><span class="k">{{ stub.label }}</span><span class="pill soon">Maybe</span></div>
      <h3>{{ stub.title }}</h3>
      <p>{{ stub.summary }}</p>
      <div class="row" style="justify-content:space-between;margin:0;">
        <span class="meta">{{ stub.when }}</span>
        <span class="meta">Thinking about it</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  {% endfor %}
</div>
